quarely, you can walk off the court and shake someone=92s hand and say, =91=
Well done,=92=94 said Rep. Diane Russell, a Maine legislator and Sanders su=
pporter. =93If you don=92t feel like the game was working fairly, it=92s ha=
rd to do that.=94

